lemma fun_sum_commute: assumes "f 0 = 0" and "\<And>x y. f (x + y) = f x + f y" shows "f (sum g A) = (\<Sum>a\<in>A. f (g a))"
by (induct A rule: infinite_finite_induct, insert assms, auto simp add: fun_eq_iff)
